    "description": "This speedy stir fry is full of flavour. You'll pan-fry pork strips with shredded veggies, gochujang chilli paste and kimchi-style sauce. Serve with aromatic long grain rice and dig in. High in protein. Protein contributes to a growth in muscle mass.",
