    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Rinse your<strong> brown rice</strong>, add it to a pot with plenty of <strong>cold water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 20-25 min or until it's tender with a slight bite</p><p>Once cooked, drain, return it to the pot and keep covered until serving</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/kimchi-veg-and-pork-stir-fry-with-brown-rice/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a high heat</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/kimchi-veg-and-pork-stir-fry-with-brown-rice/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add your <strong>pork strips</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Cook for an initial 4-5 min or until browned</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 3 or more? Use 2 pans!</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/kimchi-veg-and-pork-stir-fry-with-brown-rice/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the pork has browned, add your <strong>shredded veg mix</strong> to the pan and cook for a further 2-3 min or until the veg has started to wilt</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/kimchi-veg-and-pork-stir-fry-with-brown-rice/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the veg has started to wilt, add your <strong>tomato paste </strong>and <strong>gochujang paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) with 1/2 tsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [3/4 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tsp] </span><strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/kimchi-veg-and-pork-stir-fry-with-brown-rice/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your<strong> soy sauce </strong>with a splash of <strong>cold water </strong>and cook for a further 2 min or until the pork is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/kimchi-veg-and-pork-stir-fry-with-brown-rice/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once cooked through stir through your <strong>kimchi ketchup </strong>\u2013 this is your <strong>kimchi, veg & pork stir fry</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/kimchi-veg-and-pork-stir-fry-with-brown-rice/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>kimchi, veg & pork stir fry </strong>with the <strong>cooked rice </strong>to the side</p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into a small bowl and turn out</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
